          <div class="ml-4">
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Building Excellence Since 2009</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-md">
          Premier structural contractors specializing in concrete and masonry construction 
